📊 Banking Sector Analysis Dashboard

📌 Project Overview

This project analyzes banking data using Power BI to understand customer behavior, transactions, and loan performance.

🛠 Tools Used

- Power BI
- Excel

📊 Dashboard Features

- Customer Overview
- Transaction Analysis
- Loan Performance
- Top Customers Analysis
- Tooltip & Drill-through features
- Interactive slicers

🔍 Key Insights

- Majority customers belong to the 30–50 age group
- Top customers contribute highest transactions
- Monthly transactions show fluctuations
- Average account balance is around 50K
- Loan default rate is moderate

💡 Recommendations

- Focus on high-value customers
- Improve loan monitoring
- Target middle-age customers
- Increase customer engagement
